<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Lean 4 Workspace</h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle">Documentation for {{totalProjects}} interconnected projects</p>
</div>

<div class="categories-grid">
  {{#each categories}}
  <a href="/category/{{slug}}" class="category-card">
    <div class="category-card-icon">
      <img src="/icons/{{slug}}.svg" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="category-card-content">
      <h2 class="category-card-title">{{name}}</h2>
      <span class="category-card-count">{{count}} projects</span>
    </div>
    <div class="category-card-footer">
      View projects
    </div>
  </a>
  {{/each}}
</div>

<div class="info-section">
  <h2>About This Workspace</h2>
  <p>
    This is a collection of Lean 4 libraries and applications organized by category.
    The projects range from low-level utilities to full-featured applications,
    all built using pure Lean 4 with minimal external dependencies.
  </p>
  <h3>Key Highlights</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GPU rendering with Metal, TUI apps with Terminus</li>
    <li><strong>Web:</strong> Full-stack web development with Loom framework</li>
    <li><strong>Data:</strong> Fact databases, FRP, optics, and more</li>
    <li><strong>Apps:</strong> Games, tools, and productivity applications</li>
  </ul>
</div>
